he data used to train the model. Systematic application of model reduction methods allows implementing this modeling principle and finding models of minimal complexity compatible with the data. Combining such models is much easier than of precursor models and leads to new model properties and predictions. {\textcopyright} 2013 Kutumova et al.; licensee BioMed Central Ltd.},
